Python code and related data for exploring the book "The Raging Tide: or, The
Black Doll's Imbroglio" by Edward Gorey.

Files in this directory:
- imbroglio.py: Main program. Run 'imbroglio.py --help'.
- tide.py: Module that maintains and navigates the text of the book.
- digraph.py: Module that maintains and explores a directed graph.
- imbroglio.txt: Text of the book.
- imbroglio.dot: DOT representation of the graph.
- imbroglio.png: Graphviz representation of the graph.

To visualize the graph using graphviz, run 'imbroglio.py --dot' and submit
the output to http://graphs.grevian.org/graph
